        {
            "type": "SECTION",
            "heading": "Section 1",
            "content": "<section>\n<p class=\"mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed\">A Founding team envisioned a full \u201cimpact ecosystem\u201d where nonprofits,\n          donors, and impact\u2011aligned investors could all meet. Initially, the mission statement looked impressive on\n          paper, but it wasn\u2019t clear how it would translate into an actual product. The risk: building an expensive\n          platform that no one quite understood or used.</p>\n</section>",
            "images": []
        },
        {
            "type": "SECTION",
            "heading": "Challenges",
            "content": "<section class=\"bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-accent\">\n<h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Challenges</h2>\n<ul class=\"space-y-3 list-disc list-inside text-gray-700\">\n<li>Is a custom, multi\u2011role web app necessary from day one, or can we start with lighter tooling?</li>\n<li>How do we design the system so each audience (nonprofit, donor, investor) instantly sees where they fit?\n          </li>\n<li>What should be tested first: fundraising flows, reporting dashboards, or investment pipelines?</li>\n<li>Which early adopters and channels will provide the most honest, useful feedback?</li>\n</ul>\n</section>",
            "images": []
        },
        {
            "type": "SECTION",
            "heading": "What PhilanthroForge Did",
            "content": "<section>\n<h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">What PhilanthroForge Did</h2>\n<ul class=\"space-y-4\">\n<li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<span class=\"text-accent font-bold mt-1\">\u2713</span>\n<span><strong>Sharper Thesis:</strong> Co\u2011created a product thesis distinguishing current capabilities vs.\n              roadmap.</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<span class=\"text-accent font-bold mt-1\">\u2713</span>\n<span><strong>Architecture Design:</strong> Designed a website with distinct paths for nonprofits, donors,\n              and investors, unified by a simple story.</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<span class=\"text-accent font-bold mt-1\">\u2713</span>\n<span><strong>Onboarding Flows:</strong> Crafted flows and explainer content to minimize cognitive\n              load.</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<span class=\"text-accent font-bold mt-1\">\u2713</span>\n<span><strong>Unified Narrative:</strong> Developed a cross\u2011channel narrative (website, email, LinkedIn,\n              etc.) that told consistent stories.</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<span class=\"text-accent font-bold mt-1\">\u2713</span>\n<span><strong>Recruitment Campaigns:</strong> Built and ran multi\u2011channel campaigns to recruit\n              nonprofits.</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<span class=\"text-accent font-bold mt-1\">\u2713</span>\n<span><strong>Feedback Loops:</strong> Defined test cohorts so the early product could evolve based on\n              real\u2011world use.</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>",
            "images": []
        },
        {
            "type": "SECTION",
            "heading": "Section 4",
            "content": "<section class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n<div class=\"bg-navy text-white p-6 rounded-lg text-center\">\n<div class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-accent mb-2\">Clarity</div>\n<div class=\"text-sm opacity-80\">Turned Complex Vision into Clear UX</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bg-navy text-white p-6 rounded-lg text-center\">\n<div class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-accent mb-2\">Credibility</div>\n<div class=\"text-sm opacity-80\">Positioned for Pilots &amp; Partnerships</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bg-navy text-white p-6 rounded-lg text-center\">\n<div class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-accent mb-2\">Flexibility</div>\n<div class=\"text-sm opacity-80\">Foundation Built for Future Growth</div>\n</div>\n</section>",
            "images": []
        },
        {
            "type": "SECTION",
            "heading": "Takeaways",
            "content": "<section>\n<h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Takeaways</h2>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 italic border-l-4 border-gray-300 pl-4 py-2\">\n          Big, ecosystem\u2011level ideas don\u2019t fail for lack of ambition; they fail because users can\u2019t see where they fit.\n          Thoughtful system design and staged testing make it possible to launch something clear today that can still\n          grow into the long\u2011term vision.\n        </p>\n</section>",
